        <code>tool-runtime-sqlite-boundary.test.ts</code>,
        <code>sqlite-runtime-crash.test.ts</code> (SIGKILL). ADR:
        <code>runtime-recovery-resolver-adr.zh-CN.md</code>. Outline:
